library(lme4)
library(ggplot2)
library(emmeans)
library(patchwork)
library(car)

options(contrasts = c("contr.sum","contr.poly"))

Male mating success

Selection coefficients

mating_mcu <- lmer(Prop1 ~ Selection + (1|Block/CageID), data = MCU_mat)
mating_mb <- lmer(Prop1 ~ Selection + (1|Block/CageID), data = MB_mat)

Plot

cu_m_grad <- summary(emmeans(mating_mcu, ~ Selection))
mb_m_grad <- summary(emmeans(mating_mb, ~ Selection))

mat_plt_df <- subset(rbind(cu_m_grad, mb_m_grad), Selection != "PJB")


plt1 <- ggplot(mat_plt_df, aes(x = Selection, y = emmean)) + 
  geom_bar(stat="identity") +
  geom_errorbar(aes(ymin=lower.CL, ymax=upper.CL), width = .04) + 
  xlab("Selection Regime") + ylab("Selection coefficients (mating success)") + ggtitle("A") +
  theme_minimal() + theme(text = element_text(size = 16))

Body size

Plot (Figure 2)

male <- subset(my_data, Treatement == "HD" & Sex == "Male")
female <- subset(my_data, Treatement == "HD" & Sex == "Female")

m <- ggplot(male, aes(Selection, Wings)) +  
  stat_summary(fun.data = "mean_cl_normal", geom = "errorbar", size = 0.3, width = 0.1) +
  stat_summary(fun = "mean", colour = "black", size = 0.8) +
  ylab("Wing length") + xlab("Population") + 
  theme_minimal(base_size = 18) + theme_classic() + ggtitle("A. Male size (wing length)") +
  theme(plot.title = element_text(size = 16)) 

f <- ggplot(female, aes(Selection, Wings)) +  
  stat_summary(fun.data = "mean_cl_normal", geom = "errorbar", size = 0.3, width = 0.1) +
  stat_summary(fun = "mean", colour = "black", size = 0.8) +
  ylab("Wing length") + xlab("Population") + 
  theme_minimal(base_size = 18) + theme_classic() + ggtitle("B. Female size (wing length)") +
  theme(plot.title = element_text(size = 16)) 

mt <- ggplot(male, aes(Selection, Thorax)) +  
  stat_summary(fun.data = "mean_cl_normal", geom = "errorbar", size = 0.3, width = 0.1) +
  stat_summary(fun = "mean", colour = "black", size = 0.8) +
  ylab("Thorax length") + xlab("Population") + 
  theme_minimal(base_size = 18) + theme_classic() + ggtitle("C. Male size (thorax length)") +
  theme(plot.title = element_text(size = 16)) 

ft <- ggplot(female, aes(Selection, Thorax)) +  
  stat_summary(fun.data = "mean_cl_normal", geom = "errorbar", size = 0.3, width = 0.1) +
  stat_summary(fun = "mean", colour = "black", size = 0.8) +
  ylab("Thorax length") + xlab("Population") + 
  theme_minimal(base_size = 18) + theme_classic() + ggtitle("D. Female size (thorax length)") +
  theme(plot.title = element_text(size = 16)) 


(m + scale_x_discrete(labels = c("Crowded", "Control")) + mt + scale_x_discrete(labels = c("Crowded", "Control"))) / 
  (f + scale_x_discrete(labels = c("Crowded", "Control")) + ft + scale_x_discrete(labels = c("Crowded", "Control")))
